        "timestamp": 1686375269
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I don't think cross-posting is wrong,  it's just nice to let people know about it.  (At least in one direction, e.g. mentioning the MO question here.)</p>",
        "id": 365022480,
        "sender_full_name": "Mike Shulman",
